OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1773079566
OL,3,CPolice name man, 28, killed in
OL,4,Csuspected murder at railway station
OL,6,FPolice have named a man believed to
OL,7,Fhave been murdered at Tamworth railway
OL,8,Fstation as 28-year-old Dylan
OL,9,FFitzpatrick from Birmingham.
OL,11,FPolice were called to the station at
OL,12,Faround 2.20am on Sunday 8 March to
OL,13,Freports of an unresponsive man in the
OL,14,Fstation's car park.
OL,16,FA man, 27, from Birmingham was
OL,17,Farrested on suspicion of murder in
OL,18,FSutton Coldfield on Monday 9 March and
OL,19,Fremains in custody.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/4
