PN,37402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1773079566
OL,3,CPolice name man, 28, killed in
OL,4,Csuspected murder at railway station
OL,6,FA woman, 28, who was arrested shortly
OL,7,Fafter the incident has been released
OL,8,Ffrom custody with no further action to
OL,9,Fbe taken against her.
OL,11,FParamedics treated Mr Fitzpatrick for
OL,12,Fserious injuries 'consistent with
OL,13,Fbeing struck by a vehicle'. He died at
OL,14,Fthe scene.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/4
