CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1773079566
OL,3,CPolice name man, 28, killed in
OL,4,Csuspected murder at railway station
OL,6,FBTP Detective Inspector Marvin Bruno
OL,7,Fsaid: "This arrest follows extensive
OL,8,Fovernight enquiries and marks a
OL,9,Fsignificant step in our investigation
OL,10,Finto the death of Dylan Fitzpatrick.
OL,11,FWe are not looking for anyone else in
OL,12,Fconnection at this time.
OL,14,F"Dylan's family are being supported by
OL,15,Fspecially trained officers, and we ask
OL,16,Fthat their privacy is respected as
OL,17,Fthey process the loss of their loved
OL,18,Fone.
OL,26,@oD@GOUvD@AOU
